title: Sens. Coons and Blackburn, Biden 2020 Support

description:
Guests: Mario Parker, Bloomberg White House reporter, Matt Borges, Founder of Right Side PAC and former Ohio Republican Party Chairman, Tennessee Republican Senator Marsha Blackburn, and Delaware Democratic Senator Chris Coons.
